# ğŸŒ Global Hotel Review Analysis (2015â€“2017)

### ğŸ§  Overview
This project analyzes over **515,000 hotel reviews** from travelers around the world between **2015 and 2017**.  
It integrates **Python**, **R**, and **Tableau** to uncover global patterns in **guest satisfaction**, **sentiment**, and **traveler behavior**.

The analysis identifies key insights on:
- Differences in hotel ratings across **nationalities**
- Variation in **sentiment** across **traveler types** (e.g., business, couple, solo)
- Long-term trends in **average hotel scores**
- Global **rating distribution** visualized on an interactive world map

